import requests
from bs4 import BeautifulSoup

url = "https://www.hltv.org/matches/2363465/godsent-vs-fnatic-iem-dallas-2023-europe-closed-qualifier"
response = requests.get(url)
soup = BeautifulSoup(response.text, "html.parser")

# Teams playing
teams_playing = [team.text for team in soup.select(".teamName")]

# Score of each team
team_scores = [int(score.text) for score in soup.select(".team .score")]

# Players of each team
team_players = [[player.text for player in team.select(".statsPlayerName")] for team in soup.select(".totalstats")]

# Maps played
maps_played = [map.text for map in soup.select(".map-name-holder")]

# Score in each map
map_scores = [[int(score.text) for score in map_score.select(".results-team-score")] for map_score in soup.select(".results")]

# Match stats
match_stats = []
for team in soup.select(".totalstats"):
    team_stats = []
    for player in team.select("tr:not(.header-row)"):
        player_stats = {
            "name": player.select_one(".statsPlayerName").text,
            "kd": player.select_one(".kd").text,
            "plus_minus": player.select_one(".plus-minus").text,
            "adr": float(player.select_one(".adr").text),
            "kast": player.select_one(".kast").text,
            "rating": float(player.select_one(".rating").text),
        }
        team_stats.append(player_stats)
    match_stats.append(team_stats)

# Time and date
time_and_date = soup.select_one(".timeAndDate").text.strip()

# Event
event = soup.select_one(".event-name").text.strip()


# Print extracted information
print("Teams playing:", teams_playing)
print("Score of each team:", team_scores)
print("Players of each team:", team_players)
print("Maps played:", maps_played)
print("Score in each map:", map_scores)
print("Match stats:", match_stats)

# Print extracted information
print("Time and Date:", time_and_date)
print("Event:", event)

from selenium import webdriver
# Path to Chrome WebDriver
chrome_driver_path = "./chromedriver"

# Set up the Chrome WebDriver
options = webdriver.ChromeOptions()
options.headless = False
driver = webdriver.Chrome(executable_path=chrome_driver_path, options=options)

# Open the webpage
url = "https://www.hltv.org/matches/2363465/godsent-vs-fnatic-iem-dallas-2023-europe-closed-qualifier"
driver.get(url)

# Get the page source
html = driver.page_source

# Close the driver
driver.quit()
